\c 13
\s Jobho anofunga kuti wakarurama
\p
\v 1 Tarirai, zvese ziso rangu raona, nzeve yangu yanzwa uye yazvinzwisisa.
\v 2 Zvichienderana neruzivo rwenyu, iniwo ndinoziva, handisi pasi penyu.
\v 3 Asi ini ndichataura kune Wemasimbaose, uye ndinoshuva kunzwisisana naMwari.
\v 4 Asi imwi munodzudzura nenhema, mese muri varapi pasina.
\v 5 Haiwa! Dai muchinyarara zvachose! Zvino zvichava kwamuri uchenjeri!
\p
\v 6 Inzwai kuzvidavira kwangu, uye teererai kugakava ramiromo yangu.
\v 7 Muchataurira Mwri nezvakaipa here, nekumutaurira nekunyengera?
\v 8 Muchagamuchira chiso chake, nekumukakavadzira here?
\v 9 Zvichava zvakanaka here paanokunzverai? Kana muchanyengera here semunonyengera munhu?
\v 10 Zvirokwazvo achakutsiurai, kana pakavanda muchigamuchira zviso.
\v 11 Ukuru hwake haungakutyityidzirii, nekutyisa kwake kukakuwirai here?
\v 12 Zvirangaridzo zvenyu itsumo dzemadota, zvitaviro zvenyu zvitaviro zvevhu.
\p
\v 13 Nyararai, ndiregei, kuti nditaure ini, chipi nechipi chigondiwira.
\v 14 Zvino ndichatorerei nyama yangu mumazino angu? nemweya wangu ndiise muruoko rwangu?
\v 15 Kunyange akandiuraya, ndichatarisira iye. Asi ndichamiririra nzira dzangu pamberi pake.
\v 16 Ndiyewo achava ruponeso rwangu, nokuti munyepedzeri haangauyi pamberi pake.
\p
\v 17 Inzwai zvakanaka kutaura kwangu, kuparidza kwangu kupinde nzeve dzenyu.
\v 18 Tarirai zvino, ndarongedza mhaka yangu; ndinoziva kuti ndicharuramisirwa.
\v 19 Ndianiko achaita nharo neni? Nokuti zvino ndinganyarara hangu, ndikafa.
\v 20 Asi regai henyu kundiitira zvinhu zviviri, ipapo handingavandi pamberi penyu.
\v 21 Bvisai ruoko rwenyu kure neni; kutyisa kwenyu kurege kundivhundusa.
\v 22 Ipapo mudane imi, ini ndichapindura; kana ini nditaure hangu, imwi mundipindure.
\v 23 Zvakaipa zvangu nezvivi zvangu zvinganiko? Ndizivisei kudarika kwangu nechivi changu.
\v 24 Munovanzireiko chiso chenyu, muchiti ndiri muvengi wenyu?
\v 25 Munoda kuvhundusa shizha rinopepereswa here? Munoda kudzingana namakoto akaoma here?
\v 26 Munotonga zvinhu zvinovava pamusoro pangu, munondidyisa nhaka yezvakaipa Zvujaya hwangu;
\v 27 munomana makumbo angu mumatanda, nokucherekedza nzira dzangu dzese; munotarira tsoka dzamakumbo angu muganhu;
\v 28 kunyange ndakafanana nechinhu chakaora chinopera, senguvo yapedzwa nezvifusi.
